Class GymOwnerService

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.business.GymOwnerService
All Implemented Interfaces:
GymOwnerServiceInterface
public class GymOwnerService extends Object implements GymOwnerServiceInterface
This class implements the GymOwnerServiceInterface and provides methods to manage gym owner-related operations such as creating a gym owner, adding gym centers, showing gym centers, and editing slots.
